<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>23</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>wǒ yào gē sòng wǒ yào zàn měi 迦南23</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ yào gē sòng, wǒ yào zàn měi, wú lùn zài tiān yá hé hǎi jiǎo;
 wǒ yào chēng xiè, wǒ yào chuán yáng, wú lùn shì shùn jìng hé nì jìng.
 yīn wǒ de xīn zhōng yǒu yī wèi jiào zhǔ, tā shì wǒ shēng mìng de yuán tóu,
 bǎ wǒ dài xiàng píng ān de lù shàng, wǒ xīn xiàng huó shuǐ liú
 shǐ wǒ qǐ sǐ huí shēng, jì xù lēi mǎ, méi yǒu diào xià yuān yuān yōu gǔ.
 wǒ xīn duō jī dòng, xiàng hé liú bēn téng, jìn bù zhù yào zàn měi huān hū!
 yuàn wǒ zàn měi, huān hū de shēng yīn, xiǎng biàn zhěng gè huán qiú,
 ràng rén men dōu zhī dào, wǒ yǒu yī wèi jiào zhǔ, jiù shì yé sū.</lyrics>
</song>